<HEAD>Bush Becomes London Bookies' Favorite</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Vice President George Bush's Super Tuesday triumph
makes him the favorite to win the presidency, at odds of 4-to-9,
