<1ST_LINE>r a AM-DigestBriefs     03-09 0804</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Digest Briefs,0829</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: This package does not contain the following items from the
News Digest: UNDATED _ Politcal Rdp; WASHINGTON _ The Rest of the
Way; WASHINGTON _ If He Were White; WASHINGTON _ Campaign Money;
GAZA CITY, Occupied West Bank _ Israel-Resign; FORT CAMPBELL, Ky. _
